# {{projectName}}

A [Box Framework](https://github.com/sajjadbzrn/box) project — batteries-included backend for Bun & Cloudflare Workers.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Start development server (with hot-reload)
bun dev
```

The server will start at **http://localhost:3000**.

## Available Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `bun dev` | Start dev server with hot-reload |
| `bun test` | Run tests |
| `bun typecheck` | Type-check without emitting |
| `bun boxfw:update` | Update all BoxFW packages to latest |
{{#if hasDrizzle}}
| `bun db:generate` | Generate Drizzle migrations |
| `bun db:migrate` | Run database migrations |
{{/if}}

## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/` | Welcome message |
| `GET` | `/health` | Health check |
{{#if hasValidator}}
| `GET` | `/hello?name=World` | Zod validation example |
{{/if}}
{{#if hasDrizzle}}
| `GET` | `/users` | List all users |
{{/if}}
{{#if hasOpenapi}}
| `GET` | `/openapi.json` | OpenAPI spec |
{{/if}}
{{#if hasAuth}}
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Login |
| `GET` | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user |
{{/if}}

{{#if hasDrizzle}}
## Database

```bash
# Generate migration after schema changes
bun db:generate

# Run pending migrations
bun db:migrate
```

Schema files are in `drizzle/schema.ts`.
{{/if}}

{{#if hasI18n}}
## i18n

Locales are in `locales/`. Supported languages:
- **English** (`en`)
- **Farsi** (`fa`)
{{/if}}

{{#if hasCloudflare}}
## Deploy to Cloudflare Workers

```bash
bunx wrangler deploy
```
{{/if}}

